Application Description: THE GOTLAND MUSEUM is the Mecca of Gotland's cultural history and is run by the association Friends of the Historical Museum. The museum has a broad operation, with several independent museums. The Historical Museum is the county's flagship of cultural history and Gotland's Art Museum presents contemporary art combined with crafts and design.The Visby ruins, the rural museums Norrby, Kattlund and Petes is also included under The Gotland Museum organisation.Read moreCollapse.
